# Copy to .env.local and adjust. MeldePilot is a thin read-only client over the
# deterministic tarifhub serving API (L1) and the TarifIQ rule engine (L2). It never
# computes or stores a billing value, and submits no report without human sign-off.

# --- Deterministic backend (L1 TarifCore / FastAPI serving service) ---
# Base URL of the serving API. Used SERVER-SIDE only; never exposed to the browser.
#   local uv run uvicorn tarifhub_serving.main:app --port 8000 -> http://localhost:8000
#   in-cluster (Helm)     -> http://tarifhub-serving:8000
SERVING_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000

# --- Intelligence backend (L2 TarifIQ) ---
# Base URL of the TarifIQ service for cross-walk / rule lookups used while mapping reports.
#   local                 -> http://localhost:8070
#   in-cluster (Helm)     -> http://tarifhub-intelligence:8070
TARIFIQ_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8070

# --- LLM routing for mapping/narrative assist (data sovereignty) ---
# Any LLM-assisted mapping/narrative sends ONLY de-identified context (built by
# lib/deident.ts), routed by the backend via an EU-resident managed model (AWS Bedrock EU
# / Vertex AI EU). Patient identifiers never leave Swiss infrastructure. Operator context:
# LLM_PROVIDER=bedrock-eu            # or: vertex-eu
# LLM_REGION=eu-central-1
